            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="meta-taskdescription" metaValue="The Fiori Tile allows for the display and management of all bills of material (BOMs). With the available filters, existing BOMs can be easily found and viewed, necessary details can be accessed, and various actions such as copying, deleting BOMs, or assigning change records can be performed. There is also the option to create new BOMs, whether classical or alternative, and to add relevant components along with the required data."/>
